<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉nạ mạsẖy wnwrk qdạmy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̉nạ mạsẖy wnwrk qdạmy .. wklạmk nwry fy ạ̉yạmy
 ạ̹blys ạ̹n kạn ytḥdạny .. rạḥ ạ̉dwsh bdm ạlly fdạny
 ạlqrạr- ạ̉nạ mạsẖy wḥbk ly mnạr .. wṣlybk ʿdạny mn ạlnạr
 2- ạ̉nạ mạsẖy mạdạm ạ̹nt mʿạyạ .. wạlhdf ạ̉hw wạḍḥ jwạyạ
 fy ṭryqy bạrạjʿ kẖṭwạty .. wbạtạbʿ ṣwtk fy ḥyạty
 3- ạ̉nạ mạsẖy wdạys ʿly̱ ạ̉lmy .. wṣlybk fwqy ṣbḥ ʿlmy
 fy ṭryqy ạ̉nạ lạzm ạ̉tạ̉lm .. twhbny ậlạmk ạ̉tʿlm
 4- ạ̉nạ mạsẖy wṣwtk ʿzạny .. mn rwḥk yạ yswʿ ạ̹mlạny
 tsbyḥk yʿly̱ fy msẖwạry .. whtạfk yḥlạly fy dạry
 5- ạ̉nạ mạsẖy msạfr lnhạyẗ .. whạsyb ạlʿạlm dh wrạyạ
 ạlywm ạlrạyḥ msẖ rạjʿ .. bsẖryẗ wmlyạnẗ mwạjʿ</lyrics>
<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
<hymn_number>7376</hymn_number>
</song>